      "source": [
        "# NamOS Trainer\n",
        "\n",
        "Multi-rate conditioning trainer for NAM models.\n",
        "\n",
        "**What this does:**\n",
        "- Takes pre-trained 1-channel `.nam` models\n",
        "- Expands them to 2-channel (audio + sample rate conditioning)\n",
        "- Fine-tunes at 96kHz and 192kHz for better high-sample-rate performance\n",
        "\n",
        "**Upload order:**\n",
        "1. **DI file** — your dry input signal (e.g. `input.wav`)\n",
        "2. **Pre-trained models** — `.nam` files to expand\n",
        "3. **Capture files** — `.wav` reamp recordings matching each model\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
